<div class="container login_join findpassword">
   <div class="template-account__header">
      회원가입
   </div>
   <div class="template-account__wrapper findpassword">
      <div class="template-account__left"></div>
      <%- include ("./menu/index.ejs",{state:11}) %>
      <div class="template-account__content">
         <div class="template-login__content">
            <div class="template-account__text_hdtype_1 alert title" style='display:none'>
               <div class="rte">
                 <p class='error'></p>
               </div>
            </div>
            <div class='section'>
               <form method="post" action="/account/login" id="customer_login" accept-charset="UTF-8">
                  <div class=" label-block input-block id">
                     <label class="form-group__label subtitle-2 is-hidden" for="CustomerId">
                     </label>
                     <input id="CustomerId" autocapitalize="off" autocomplete="off" autofocus="" name="customer[id]" placeholder="아이디" required="" spellcheck="false" type="text"  data-need="id" data-need-length="8">
                  </div>
                  <div class=" label-block input-block name">
                     <label class="form-group__label subtitle-2 is-hidden" for="CustomerEmail">
                     </label>
                     <input id="CustomerName"  autocapitalize="off" autocomplete="off" autofocus="" name="customer[text]" placeholder="이름" required="" spellcheck="false" type="text"  data-need="name" data-need-length="4">
                  </div>
                  <div class=" label-block input-block birthday">
                     <label class="form-group__label subtitle-2 is-hidden" for="CustomerPassword">
                     </label>
                     <input id="CustomerBirthday"  autocapitalize="off" autocomplete="off" autofocus="" name="customer[password]" placeholder="생년월일" required="" spellcheck="false" type="text" data-need="birthday">
                  </div>
                  <div class="text-block sub-description ">
                     <p class='m-font-13'>생년월일 8자리를 입력해주세요 (예. 20150115)</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="button-block auth-join-button loading-wrap">
                     <input class="button button--primary button--block button--large m-font-14" data-form-submit="doAuthJoinButton" type="button" value="인증하기">
                     <div class="loader">
                        <div class="smiley-spin">
                           <svg class="icon icon--medium icon__smiley" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M8 15.5a7.5 7.5 0 110-15 7.5 7.5 0 010 15zm0-1a6.5 6.5 0 100-13 6.5 6.5 0 000 13zM4.947 9.776l-.894.448a4.413 4.413 0 007.894 0l-.894-.448a3.413 3.413 0 01-6.106 0zM9.5 5h1v2h-1V5zm-3 0h-1v2h1V5z"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                     </div>
                  </div>

               </form>
            </div>

            


            <div class='line-block content-line'>
            </div>

            <div class='text section'>
               <div class="text-block ">
                  <p>휴대폰으로 인증하신 경우, <a href="#" style='text-decoration: underline;'>여기</a>를 눌러주세요.</p>
               </div>
            </div>

            <div class='section'>
               <div class="table-block input-table">
                  <div >
                     <input id="CustomerPassword" name="customer[password]" placeholder="휴대폰번호 입력" required="" type="text" data-need="phone" data-need-length="10" numberOnly>
                  </div>
                  <div >
                     <input type="button" class="button duplicatebtn" value="인증번호 받기">
                  </div>
               </div>
               <div class="table-block input-table">
                  <div>
                     <input id="CustomerPassword" name="customer[password]" placeholder="인증번호 입력" required="" type="text" data-need="authnumber" data-need-length="6" numberOnly>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                     <input type="button" class="button duplicatebtn" value="휴대폰 인증">
                  </div>
               </div>
               <div class="text-block sub-description time">
                  <p class='m-font-13'>유효시간 <span>03:00</span></p>
               </div>
            </div>
               

            <div class='text section'>
               <div class="text-block infolist">
                  <ul>
                     <li>휴대폰으로 발송된 인증번호를 유효시간 내에 입력해주시고, 인증번호가 도착하지 않을 시 재발송을 해주세요.</li>
                     <li>입력한 휴대폰번호는 보안 시스템을 통해 안전하게 관리됩니다.</li>
                  </ul>
               </div>
            </div>

         </div>
      </div>
   </div>
</div>